      "title": "三天赚出第一桶金",
      "description": "你从2026年醒来，发现自己回到了2010年。亲戚逼着卖老房子，父亲住院等着交押金...",
      "year": 2010,
      "chapterNumber": 1,
      "mainGoal": "3天内赚出第一桶金，保住老房子",
      "goalTarget": {
        "type": "complete_events",
        "value": 7
      },
      "scenes": ["old_house", "street_corner"],
      "events": [
        {
          "id": "event_ch1_wakeup",
          "type": "main",
          "title": "重返2010",
          "description": "从2026年醒来，发现回到了2010年",
          "dialogue": [
            {
              "speaker": "旁白",
              "text": "2026年，35岁的你，事业受挫，负债累累...",
              "duration": 3000
            },
            {
              "speaker": "旁白",
              "text": "一次意外后，你睁开眼，看到了熟悉又陌生的老房子...",
              "duration": 3000
            },
            {
              "speaker": "父亲",
              "text": "孩子，你醒了？家里正好需要钱...",
              "emotion": "worried",
              "duration": 2000
            },
            {
              "speaker": "主角",
              "text": "这是...2010年？我重生了！",
              "emotion": "surprised",
              "duration": 2000
            }
          ],
          "requirements": [],
          "triggerOnce": true,
          "priority": 10
        },
        {
          "id": "event_ch1_father_illness",
          "type": "main",
          "title": "先交住院押金",
          "description": "父亲病倒，家里需要先交一笔住院押金",
          "dialogue": [
            {
              "speaker": "旁白",
              "text": "父亲突然病倒，被送进了医院...",
              "duration": 2500
            },
            {
              "speaker": "医生",
              "text": "先交一笔押金，后面的费用再想办法...",
              "duration": 2000
            },
            {
              "speaker": "主角",
              "text": "先把押金交上，后面的我来想办法。",
              "emotion": "worried",
              "duration": 2000
            },
            {
              "speaker": "母亲",
              "text": "家里现在只有不到500元...",
              "emotion": "sad",
              "duration": 2000
            }
          ],
          "requirements": [
            {
              "type": "item",
              "value": {
                "itemId": "money_2",
                "level": 2,
                "count": 1
              }
            }
          ],
          "rewards": {
            "connections": 1
          },
          "triggerOnce": true,
          "priority": 8,
          "nextEvents": ["event_ch1_relative_debt"]
        },
        {
          "id": "event_ch1_relative_debt",
          "type": "main",
          "title": "亲戚催债",
          "description": "亲戚上门催债，让还钱",
          "dialogue": [
            {
              "speaker": "势利亲戚",
              "text": "哟，听说你们家需要钱啊？那笔5000块的债，什么时候能还？",
              "emotion": "arrogant",
              "duration": 3000
            },
            {
              "speaker": "势利亲戚",
              "text": "别以为能拖着，实在不行就把这老房子卖了抵债吧！",
              "emotion": "threatening",
              "duration": 2500
            },
            {
              "speaker": "主角",
              "text": "（心里想着：前世我们家就是这个时候卖了老房子...）",
              "emotion": "angry",
              "duration": 2500
            },
            {
              "speaker": "主角",
              "text": "给我3天时间，我会还上这笔钱！",
              "emotion": "determined",
              "duration": 2000
            },
            {
              "speaker": "势利亲戚",
              "text": "3天？哈哈哈哈，就凭你？行啊，我等着看！",
              "emotion": "mocking",
              "duration": 2500
            }
          ],
          "requirements": [
            {
              "type": "event_complete",
              "value": "event_ch1_father_illness"
            }
          ],
          "rewards": {
            "cash": 50
          },
          "triggerOnce": true,
          "priority": 9
        },
        {
