          "type": "event",
          "title": "第一次摆摊",
          "description": "在街边第一次摆摊卖东西",
          "dialogue": [
            {
              "speaker": "旁白",
              "text": "你想起前世，这个时候夜市经济刚开始火...",
              "duration": 2500
            },
            {
              "speaker": "主角",
              "text": "我有前世记忆，知道什么能卖得好！",
              "emotion": "confident",
              "duration": 2000
            },
            {
              "speaker": "旁白",
              "text": "你翻出了家里的旧纸箱，准备了一些小商品...",
              "duration": 2500
            },
            {
              "speaker": "主角",
              "text": "袜子、发卡、小玩具...先从这些开始吧！",
              "emotion": "motivated",
              "duration": 2000
            }
          ],
          "requirements": [
            {
              "type": "event_complete",
              "value": "event_ch1_relative_debt"
            },
            {
              "type": "item",
              "value": {
                "itemId": "product_1",
                "level": 1,
                "count": 2
              }
            }
          ],
          "rewards": {
            "cash": 100
          },
          "triggerOnce": true,
          "priority": 7
        },
        {
          "id": "event_ch1_first_earnings",
          "type": "event",
          "title": "第一笔收入",
          "description": "摆摊赚到了第一笔钱",
          "dialogue": [
            {
              "speaker": "旁白",
              "text": "傍晚，你在街边摆起了小摊...",
              "duration": 2000
            },
            {
              "speaker": "学生顾客",
              "text": "这个发卡怎么卖？",
              "emotion": "casual",
              "duration": 1500
            },
            {
              "speaker": "主角",
              "text": "3块钱一个，5块钱两个！",
              "emotion": "smiling",
              "duration": 1500
            },
            {
              "speaker": "旁白",
              "text": "第一单！你心里充满了激动...",
              "duration": 2000
            },
            {
              "speaker": "主角",
              "text": "第一天晚上就赚了200多！这个方向是对的！",
              "emotion": "excited",
              "duration": 2500
            }
          ],
          "requirements": [
            {
              "type": "event_complete",
              "value": "event_ch1_first_business"
            },
            {
              "type": "item",
              "value": {
                "itemId": "product_2",
                "level": 2,
                "count": 1
              }
            }
          ],
          "rewards": {
            "cash": 200,
            "reputation": 2
          },
          "triggerOnce": true,
          "priority": 6
        },
        {
          "id": "event_ch1_regular_customers",
          "type": "event",
          "title": "老客户带人排队",
          "description": "老客户认可你的货，带来一批新顾客",
          "dialogue": [
            {
              "speaker": "老客户",
              "text": "你这货实在，我带几个朋友过来看看。",
              "emotion": "friendly",
              "duration": 2000
            },
            {
              "speaker": "旁白",
              "text": "小摊前第一次排起了队。",
              "duration": 2000
            },
            {
              "speaker": "势利亲戚",
              "text": "怎么会有这么多人买他的东西？",
              "emotion": "shocked",
              "duration": 2000
            },
            {
              "speaker": "主角",
              "text": "生意不是靠嘴说，是靠人一单一单认出来的。",
              "emotion": "calm",
              "duration": 2500
            }
          ],
          "requirements": [
            {
              "type": "event_complete",
              "value": "event_ch1_first_earnings"
